      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRANCING PAT (4) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at his last six runs. Last time finished 3rd over 350m at Goulburn beaten 5 lengths (20.06) behind Cawbourne Focus in a NG on July 3. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Winning claims. TIGGERLONG BINGO (5) has a strong record this track and trip with 21 wins and four placings from 30 starts. Hit the frame latest (18.92) when second at Temora in a NG. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. GOT A MESSAGE (1) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 5 at this track. Expected to do much better this time. CAWBOURNE MAXX (2) can play a role in the finish without surprising.",
